npx playwright test  => running all the tests
 npx playwright test  --headed => running all the tests in headed mode
 npx playwright test --project=chromium => running tests in specific browser
 npx playwright test --project=chromium --headed => running tests in specific browser in headed mode
 npx playwright test --project=chromium --project=firefox => running tests in multiple browsers
npx playwright test tests/day2.spec.js  => running specific test file
npx playwright test -g "valid credentials"  => running specific test by its name

npx playwright test  tests/day2.spec.js --headed  --debug 